</div>
                        
                        <p>Things are likely to get a lot worse in Bloomington before they get any better, which is a testament to the one things athletic departments need far more than the hottest coach in the market&mdash;patience. </p>
<p>An answer like Harbaugh rarely comes around, and it just may be in the interest of a program to wait for its luck to come back around. </p>
<p>Just ask the Blue Devils.</p>

